---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Better Than A Fence — honest GPS dog fence reviews from a real dog owner who spent $5,200+ testing every system on the market." lcpImage="/images/Collie-Looking-At-Owner-Resize-1024x682.jpg">

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container content-width">
      <h1>About Better Than A Fence</h1>
      <p class="about-lead">I'm not a corporation. I'm not sponsored by any GPS fence company. I'm just a dog owner who spent <strong>$5,200+</strong> learning which GPS dog fences actually work — and which ones almost got my dog killed.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-body">
    <div class="container content-width">
      <div class="about-image-wrap">
        <img src="/images/Collie-Looking-At-Owner-Resize-1024x682.jpg" alt="Border Collie looking at owner" width="1024" height="682" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" />
      </div>

      <h2>My Story</h2>
      <p>Three years ago, my Border Collie Max nearly got killed on Highway 34 because a "5-star rated" GPS fence thought he was safely in our backyard.</p>
      <p>After that terrifying moment, I went on a mission. Over the next 18 months, I tested <strong>8+ GPS dog fence systems</strong> on my own 5-acre property — a property that presents every GPS challenge imaginable:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Heavy tree coverage on 60% of the land</li>
        <li>Metal outbuildings that interfere with signals</li>
        <li>A stream cutting through the property</li>
        <li>Elevation changes of over 100 feet</li>
        <li>Direct proximity to a busy road</li>
      </ul>
      <p>I spent thousands of dollars on cheap Amazon specials, mid-range options, and premium systems. I analyzed <strong>1,900+ verified customer reviews</strong> across multiple platforms. And I documented everything so other dog owners wouldn't have to make the same expensive mistakes I did.</p>

      <h2>What I Believe</h2>
      <p>Your dog's safety shouldn't depend on fake Amazon reviews or paid sponsorships. Every review on this site is based on <strong>real, hands-on testing</strong> in challenging real-world conditions — not a controlled laboratory.</p>
      <p>I only recommend products I personally use and trust with my own dogs' lives.</p>

      <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>In-depth reviews</strong> based on months of daily use, not weekend tryouts</li>
        <li><strong>Head-to-head comparisons</strong> tested on the same property under identical conditions</li>
        <li><strong>Honest assessments</strong> that include the bad and ugly, not just the good</li>
        <li><strong>Real cost breakdowns</strong> including hidden subscription fees most reviewers ignore</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>This site contains affiliate links. If you click through and make a purchase, I may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This helps me continue testing new products and publishing honest reviews. I never let affiliate relationships influence my recommendations — if a product doesn't work, I'll tell you.</p>

      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>Have questions about GPS dog fences? Need help deciding which system is right for your property? Feel free to reach out at <a href="mailto:contact@betterthanafence.com">contact@betterthanafence.com</a>.</p>

      <div class="about-cta">
        <a href="/spoton-vs-halo" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Read My #1 Recommendation &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 60px 0 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--off-white) 0%, var(--white) 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-lead {
    font-size: 1.1875rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-body {
    padding: 40px 0 80px;
  }
  .about-image-wrap {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .about-image-wrap img {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    width: 100%;
  }
  .about-body h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gray-100);
  }
  .about-body p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .about-body ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .about-body li {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--gray-100);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero { padding: 40px 0 24px; }
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 1.875rem; }
  }
</style>
